<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Course Rejection Notification</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 40px auto;
            background-color: #fff;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .header {
            border-bottom: 2px solid #006ca5;
            padding-bottom: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .header h1 {
            color: #006ca5;
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 24px;
        }
        .content {
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        .highlight {
            color: #d9534f;
            margin: 0;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .content p {
            margin: 15px 0;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 30px;
            border-top: 1px solid #ddd;
            padding-top: 15px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #777;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Course Rejection Notification</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Dear Instructor,</p>
            <p>Your course <span class="highlight"><%= courseName %></span> has been rejected for the following reason:</p>
            <p><h3><%= reason %></h3></p>
            <p>Best regards,</p>
            <p>The Admin Team</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; <%= year %> EazyLearN. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
